data.description: Welcome to this 4 Bedroom 2 bath house in the county of Alamosa. This home is sitting on 35 acres of land and has a beautiful view of Mt. Blanca. This home also features 2 Greenhouses and a large steel barn. Greenhouses were built back in 2020. The roof and sidings were replaced in 2021. Interior was painted in 2021. The property has sole well rights and is a domestic well. This allows for 3 single family residences, watering livestock and an acre of lawn and garden.
